high_descs: Grab the pan on the stove
turn around, walk to the sink
put the pan in the sink, wash the pan with water, take the pan
turn around, walk back to the stove
put the pan down on the bottom right stove
anns.task_desc: wash the pan from the stove, put it back on the stove

high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the stove.
Pick the pan up from the back burner of the stove.
Go to the right and stand in front of the sink.
Put the pan in the sink and turn the water on and then off and then take the pan out of the sink.
Go to the left and stand in front of the stove.
Put the pan on the right side of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan on the stove.

high_descs: Turn to the stove on your left.
Pick up the pan on the back left burner of the stove.
Turn around, walk a bit, and turn left to reach the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink, then pick it up again.
Turn around and walk back to the stove.
Place the pan on the front right burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed pan on a stove.
